{"tid":1647994,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣亂撚到仆街","createTime":"2019-10-12T04:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T04:26:59.000Z","uid":314119,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"35790d7b5d0cb7a8c0e5ee927d7542bf05b76d9e","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:00:13.000Z","msg":"可唔可以集中番星期一至五集會<br />\n六日開花或者遊行<br />\n留番一至兩個星期宣傳<br />\n同埋 唔好成日轉場<br />\n<br />\n個重點係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔知究竟要出邊個活動</span><br />\n再加上文宣臨時臨急根本就做唔切<br />\n銀髮族又唔夠時間睇文宣<br />\n結果就度度都好散<br />\n一散就容易比狗咬<br />\n<br />\n希望大家去番7月個個節奏<br />\n比番啲時間大家 去唸究竟點樣出黎<br />\n同埋個活動時間可以搞早啲 比其他人預早啲搭巴士<br />\n因為黨鐵實封<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論"},{"pid":"afe9ab970e01c07bebff75877976c8b1f662413c","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:00:37.000Z","msg":"幫推 p牌推唔到"},{"pid":"93c018bbd7cf1fb2cf59fcf47d0c1fbf1dd3a888","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:00:47.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"e08e6e0ecdd9c723d7a1400de4b64977d3d893b6","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"97f94205b719f2a400f539d4816d22faf4c163a5","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"90c3053ea7099a95b1abd51a18ba04d611f45d68","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:01:17.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"2c3e8844ba7968b7cea6853e0a0737b7f41957a6","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:01:27.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"c86719c7b6837f909889ff9a38a1fa44ddbe68d1","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T04:01:37.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"1971e75a3fb12149f45840d6b1bc2b0621c86df5","tid":1647994,"uid":314119,"lik